1. find the maximum number of viewcounts.

select MAX(Posts.ViewCount) AS max_viewcount from Posts 
  output -    10030841

2.select top 50000 * from Posts where Posts.ViewCount<10030842 ORDER BY Posts.ViewCount desc // Download -> QueryResults_1 
3.select top 50000 * from Posts where Posts.ViewCount<127402 ORDER BY Posts.ViewCount desc // Download -> QueryResults_2
4.select top 50000 * from Posts where Posts.ViewCount<74595 ORDER BY Posts.ViewCount desc // Download -> QueryResults_3
5.select top 50000 * from Posts where Posts.ViewCount<53210 ORDER BY Posts.ViewCount desc // Download -> QueryResults_4

*Note* - value 127402 for the point number 3 has come from the last value of QueryResult_1 